<tr><td style="padding:10px 0;font-family:&#x27;DM Sans&#x27;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#344054;font-weight:500;width:55%;vertical-align:top">Fecha programada</td><td style="padding:10px 0;font-family:Poppins, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1A1A2E;font-weight:600;text-align:right;vertical-align:top;white-space:nowrap">31 de mayo de 2026</td></tr></tbody></table><table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;border-bottom:1px solid #E4E7EC"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:10px 0;font-family:&#x27;DM Sans&#x27;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#344054;font-weight:500;width:55%;vertical-align:top">Procesador</td><td style="padding:10px 0;font-family:Poppins, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1A1A2E;font-weight:600;text-align:right;vertical-align:top;white-space:nowrap">Banco de Chile</td></tr></tbody></table><table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;border-bottom:1px solid #E4E7EC"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:10px 0;font-family:&#x27;DM Sans&#x27;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#344054;font-weight:500;width:55%;vertical-align:top">Monto neto</td><td style="padding:10px 0;font-family:Poppins, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-size:18px;color:#1A1A2E;font-weight:700;text-align:right;vertical-align:top;white-space:nowrap">$1.480.000</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table align="center" width="100%" border="0" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" role="presentation" style="text-align:center;margin:0 0 24px"><tbody><tr><td><a href="https://greenhouse.efeoncepro.com/my/payroll" style="line-height:1;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;max-width:100%;mso-padding-alt:0px;background-color:#0375db;color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Poppins, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;padding:14px 36px;border-radius:8px;text-ali